        <div class="all-categories text-center">
            <hr class="half-hr"> <h2 class="category-heading text-success" style="font-weight: 900;">Importance of Voting</h2> <hr class="half-hr">
        </div>

        <div class="container px-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                  <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Expressing Civic Duty</h5>
                      <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                      <p class="card-text">Voting is a way for citizens to actively participate in the democratic process and fulfill their civic duty.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                  <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Ensuring Representation</h5>
                      <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                      <p class="card-text">By voting, individuals contribute to the selection of representatives who will make decisions on their behalf. Voting ensures that the government reflects the will of the people.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                  <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Influencing Policies</h5>
                      <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                      <p class="card-text">Voting allows citizens to influence the development and implementation of policies. It is a means of expressing preferences on issues that matter to them.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                  <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Protecting Rights</h5>
                      <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                      <p class="card-text">Voting is a way to protect and exercise fundamental rights. It is a tool to ensure that the government respects and upholds the rights of its citizens.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                  <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Shaping the Future</h5>
                      <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                      <p class="card-text">Voting enables individuals to contribute to the direction and future of their country. It empowers people to have a say in the kind of society they want to live in.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                  <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Strengthening Democracy</h5>
                      <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                      <p class="card-text">Voting is a cornerstone of democracy. When more people participate in the electoral process, it leads to a more robust and representative democracy.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                
            </div>
        </div>

