        <div class="all-categories text-center" id="votingProcess">
          <hr class="half-hr"> <h2 class="category-heading text-success" style="font-weight: 900;">Voting Process</h2> <hr class="half-hr">
        </div>
        

        <div class="container px-5">
          <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Registration</h5>
                    <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                    <p class="card-text">Before you can vote, you usually need to register. This process involves providing personal information such as your name, address, and sometimes identification details.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Check Voter Information</h5>
                    <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                    <p class="card-text">Verify your voter registration status to ensure it is active and up-to-date.
                      Confirm your polling place or learn about early voting and mail-in ballot options.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Research Candidates and Issues</h5>
                    <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                    <p class="card-text">Familiarize yourself with the candidates running for office and the issues on the ballot.
                      Attend debates, read candidate statements, and research the pros and cons of ballot measures.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Casting Your Vote</h5>
                  <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                  <p class="card-text">On Election Day, go to your designated polling place. Bring a valid form of identification if required.
                    Follow the instructions on the voting machine or paper ballot. Some places use electronic voting machines, while others use paper ballots.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Submit Your Vote</h5>
                  <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                  <p class="card-text">After making your selections, submit your ballot according to the instructions provided.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Early Voting and Mail-In Ballots</h5>
                  <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                  <p class="card-text">Some regions offer early voting, allowing voters to cast their ballots before Election Day.
                    Mail-in or absentee voting is available in many places. Request a mail-in ballot if you cannot vote in person.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>


      <div class="all-categories text-center" id="eligibilityCriteria">
        <hr class="half-hr"> <h2 class="category-heading text-success" style="font-weight: 900;">Eligibility Criteria</h2> <hr class="half-hr">
      </div>
      

      <div class="container px-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Citizenship</h5>
                  <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                  <p class="card-text">Generally, you must be a citizen of the country in which you are voting.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Age</h5>
                  <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                  <p class="card-text">Most places require voters to be a certain age (usually 18 or older). Some jurisdictions allow pre-registration for individuals who will turn 18 before Election Day.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Residency</h5>
                  <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                  <p class="card-text">You must be a resident of the state or district where you are voting.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
            <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Criminal Record</h5>
                <hr class="greenHorizontalLine">
                <p class="card-text">In some places, individuals with felony convictions may be ineligible to vote. However, this varies by jurisdiction, and rights may be restored after completing a sentence.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>


